@package typo3/cms-install
@label [TASK] Offer to import bundled distributions during installation process
@link https://review.typo3.org/c/Packages/TYPO3.CMS/+/93485
@version ~14.2.0

From 926b9a704b81c50ab45ab7e10ed6374f63ec203a Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Benjamin Kott <benjamin.kott@outlook.com>
Date: Tue, 31 Mar 2026 11:22:11 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] [TASK] Offer to import bundled distributions during installation process

By default `theme_camino` will be offered to be imported if installed
(always installed by default in classic mode, and available
if `typo3/theme-camino` has been required in composer mode).

Resolves: #109460
Releases: main
Change-Id: I2f22f56adf0362767e795ffce0d78d25e01fef2a
Reviewed-on: https://review.typo3.org/c/Packages/TYPO3.CMS/+/93485
Tested-by: core-ci <typo3@b13.com>
Tested-by: Benjamin Franzke <ben@bnf.dev>
Reviewed-by: Benjamin Franzke <ben@bnf.dev>
Tested-by: Benni Mack <benni@typo3.org>
Reviewed-by: Benni Mack <benni@typo3.org>
---

